{"tid":360842,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊控股見左頂，玩L完","createTime":"2017-08-15T15:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T15:14:21.000Z","uid":83518,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75f9a154e08c12ad33d53d3b42ab6ac9e9d3b8a3","tid":360842,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"追沽機會黎啦！理由如下文：<br />\n<br />\n【王者終會倒下 神話幻滅】<br />\n一代股王騰訊控股(<a href=\"http://700.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F700.HK&d=d23azUcGDkfI%2FZaGypc7aY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=234a752c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">700.HK</a>)成就不少百萬富翁神話，明天(16日)將公布中期業績(截至6月底)。根據10間券商對騰訊半年純利預測，介乎270至296億元人民幣，按年增加36%至49%。<br />\n<br />\n股神巴菲特金句：「別人貪婪時，你要恐慌。」<br />\n<br />\n呢期人人都討論騰訊股價幾時見$400或$500，分析師多數睇好中期業績，呢個情況類似2007年股市瘋狂上升時。仙仔綜合6大睇淡觀點，以供大家參考。<br />\n<br />\n1. 高增長不再：上年盈利達450億，大基數之下難長期維持高增長<br />\n2. 估值過高：PE高達65倍，如無高增長，股價將受壓<br />\n3. 遊戲難長紅：手機或PC遊戲成增長點，但熱潮短，容易被取代<br />\n4. 圖表轉弱：$333見頂後，只回補下跌裂口，隨即大幅回跌<br />\n5. 散戶進取：網上發現不少散戶表示已於$300至$320購入騰訊<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100Cin/posts/1417904334971675:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100Cin%2Fposts%2F1417904334971675%3A0&d=d23azUcGDkfI%2FZaGypc7aY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4b29e8d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100Cin/posts/1417904334971675:0</a>"},{"pid":"fdc2b6d4fcb8d8a0d1037ed6482050bc5f4148c4","tid":360842,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:38:25.000Z","msg":"100仙財經娛樂雜誌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7267a3ee61a99a3eb1f05cdd0ed5d8edc3db0c9","tid":360842,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"美國科技股夠貴都大把上升空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6026002f8c4dfeab4e7d265d93a26eeaceacf8f0","tid":360842,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT